{"tha-ap214:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap214:0.2":"Hatthivagga ","tha-ap214:0.3":"Panadhidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap214:1.1":"“Arannikassa isino, ","tha-ap214:1.2":"cirarattatapassino; ","tha-ap214:1.3":"Vuddhassa bhavitattassa, ","tha-ap214:1.4":"adasim panadhim aham. ","tha-ap214:2.1":"Tena kammena dvipadinda, ","tha-ap214:2.2":"lokajettha narasabha; ","tha-ap214:2.3":"Dibbayanam anubhomi, ","tha-ap214:2.4":"pubbakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap214:3.1":"Catunnavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap214:3.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap214:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap214:3.4":"panadhissa idam phalam. ","tha-ap214:4.1":"Sattasattatito kappe, ","tha-ap214:4.2":"attha asimsu khattiya; ","tha-ap214:4.3":"Suyana nama namena, ","tha-ap214:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap214:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap214:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap214:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap214:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma panadhidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap214:7.1":"Panadhidayakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}